data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts an inviting open concept floor plan, perfect for modern living and entertaining. Upon entering the home, you'll be captivated by the seamless flow from the spacious living room into the elegant dining and kitchen area creating a warm and inviting ambiance for gatherings of all sizes. The kitchen is a chef's delight featuring an abundance of storage space to keep everything organized and clutter-free. The centerpiece of the kitchen is a beautiful island/breakfast bar providing both a functional workspace and a cozy spot to enjoy casual meals with loved ones. The master suite is a private sanctuary, offering a peaceful retreat with its own luxurious en-suite bathroom. Pamper yourself in style and comfort in this tranquil space. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, providing ample room for family members or guests. Whether it's creating a home office, setting up a playroom for the kids, or hosting overnight visitors, these rooms offer limitless possibilities. Situated on a generous .89-acre lot this property provides plenty of space for outdoor enjoyment and recreation. Whether it's hosting BBQs, playing outdoor games, or simply enjoying the fresh air, this home is tailor-made for family get-togethers and making lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a tour today and experience the magic of this inviting and versatile property!
